children.description: When I set the header module to 'My Employee File'
When i go to administer time
When i click go to time off
Then the time off page is displayed
When i click create absence button
Then the create absence form is displayed
When i set the time type: Holiday Leave
Then a warning message is displayed according to absence type: Holiday Leave
When i set the start date: 18/06/2024
When i set the end date: 18/06/2024
Then a pop up message of time off approval is displayed: Your time off request was saved and is awaiting approval by Mustafa Ahmad Hammad.

testSteps.description: When the line manager reviews and approve absence request: Mustafa Ahmad Hammad, A670897, nrt2024HRIS$, ATIQULLAH AMANI, A777981, nrt2024HRIS$, Holiday Leave, 18/06/2024, 18/06/2024, 1, 1, Pending, 100104471, LINE MANAGER COMMENT, Future Events, 18/06/2024
When the employee cancels the approved absence request: ATIQULLAH AMANI, A777981, nrt2024HRIS$, Future Events, Holiday Leave, Approved, 18/06/2024

When the line manager reviews and approve the cancellation of approved absence request: Mustafa Ahmad Hammad, A670897, nrt2024HRIS$, ATIQULLAH AMANI, A777981, nrt2024HRIS$, Holiday Leave, 18/06/2024, 18/06/2024, 1, 1, Cancellation Pending, 100104471, LINE MANAGER COMMENT, Future Events, 18/06/2024
